  <title>汨罗生态环境数据管理实时发布系统</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fefefe;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #333;
      font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';
    }

    p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .wrapper {
      padding-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .top-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
      height: 40px;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 40px;
      font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';
      background-color: #16d3cc;
      background-size: cover;
    }

    .center-content {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 16px;
    }


    .text {
      text-indent: 20px;
    }

    .download-box {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
      height:150px;
    }

    .download-box a {
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .download-box img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .app-icon {
      margin-top: 5px;
      float: left;
      width: 40%;
      height:150px;
    }

    .download {
      float: right;
      width: 52%;
      height:150px;
      display:table;
    }

    .footer {
      position: fixed;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      height: 40px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .dark-bg {
      position: fixed;
      display: none;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      z-index: 9999;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.75);
    }

    .dark-bg img {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .img-box {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      clear: both;
    }

    .img-box img {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .img-left, .img-right {
      float: left;
      width: 46%;
    }

    .img-right {
      float: right;
    }

    .intro {
      width: 90%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      clear: both;
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .intro ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <h3 class="top-title">系统升级公告</h3>

  <div class="center-content">
    <p class="user">尊敬的用户:</p>
    <p class="text">您好,“汨罗生态环境数据管理”已经升级，新系统增加提供了APP的发布方式，请依据下图指引安装新版软件"汨罗生态环境数据管理"APP。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="download-box">
    <div class="app-icon">
      <img src="/image/log.png" alt="logo" tppabs="http://59.172.208.250:9093/images/app-icon.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="download">
      <div style="width:100%;display:table-cell; vertical-align:middle;">
        <a id="androidDownload" href="javascript:void(0)"><img src="/image/d-and.png" alt="android下载"/></a>
        <a id="goBower" href="javascript:void(0)"><img src="/image/d-bower.png" alt="访问网页版" /></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="img-box">
    <div class="img-left">
      <img src="/image/home.jpg" alt="首页" />
    </div>
    <div class="img-right">
      <img src="/image/map.jpg" alt="地图" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="intro">
    <strong>功能介绍</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>首页：可查看汨罗市省控、国控站点最近一小时数据情况，以及过去24小时和7天数据</li>
      <li>地图：可查看汨罗市各个站点数据情况，可点击查看详情</li>
      <li>工单管理：可查看任务情况，修改任务</li>
      <li>报警：可查看汨罗市站点监测因子超标情况，以及添加任务</li>
      <li>更多：可更新版本</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    技术支持电话：400-139-7077
  </div>
</div>
<div id="darkLayout" class="dark-bg"><img src="/image/live_weixin.png" /></div>
</body>
</html>

<script type="text/javascript">
  window.onload = function () {
    var btn = document.getElementById('androidDownload');
    var iosBtn = document.getElementById('iosDownload');
    var bowerBtn = document.getElementById('goBower');
    var darkLayout = document.getElementById('darkLayout');
    btn.onclick = function (e) {
      if (isWeiXin()) {
        darkLayout.style.position = "fixed";
        darkLayout.style.display = "block";
      }
      else {
        location.href = "http://218.75.181.68:8306/mlAPP/ml.apk";
      }
    }
    bowerBtn.onclick = function (e) {
      location.href = "http://218.75.181.68:8306/mlAPP/index.html";
    }
    function isWeiXin() {
      var ua = window.navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
      if (ua.match(/MicroMessenger/i) == 'micromessenger') {
        return true;
      } else {
        return false;
      }
    }
  }
</script>